long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
ChatGPT is a genius model, that can answer your most advanced questions, however it takes a long time to navigate to it and access it.

This is why QuickGPT was created.
A simple, yet extremely handy tool to instantly satisfy any curiosity you have with a single click.

The best thing? NO data is collected by QuickGPT.

Note: The project is still relatively new, so mind potential bugs.
